         MACRO                                                                  
&L       LKREL &LOCK                                                            
.*                                                                              
.* AUTOMATE THE CALLING SEQUENCE FOR LOCKRL                                     
.*                                                                              
&L       PSET  @LOCKS,CLEAR=NO                                                  
         PMOV  @LOCKID,&LOCK                                                    
         VCALL LKREL         CALL THE ROUTINE                                   
         MEND                                                                   
